The current NT Event Log appender has no controls for setting the Event # or 
username. The appender should have the following 4 new methods added:

public void setEventID(int newId)
public int getEventID()
public void setUser(String username)
public String getUser()

This would be beneficial for users of tools which read the NT Event Log. Some 
of these tools use the Event ID number extensively, and it is unfortunate that 
this is not configurable in Log4j.
